sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client
    participant R as VllmPDRouter
    participant P as Prefill(Producer)
    participant P_ZMQ as P: SendingThread<br/>(ZMQ ROUTER)
    participant RDMA as P2P RDMA直传<br/>(Mooncake TransferEngine)
    participant D as Decode(Consumer)
    participant D_ZMQ as D: RecvingThread

    rect rgb(230,245,255)
    Note over R,D_ZMQ: ===== 初始化阶段 =====

    Note over R: 固定配置模式: 注册P/D到WorkerRegistry, 无服务发现
    R->>P: GET /health (循环等待直到200 OK)
    P-->>R: 200 OK
    R->>D: GET /health (循环等待直到200 OK)
    D-->>R: 200 OK
    R->>P: GET /query (获取engine_id)
    P-->>R: {dp_rank: {engine_id: "xxx"}}

    Note over P: register_kv_caches(): 注册KV内存到TransferEngine
    Note over P: 启动SendingThread(ZMQ ROUTER, 监听D的元数据请求)
    Note over D: register_kv_caches(): 注册KV内存到TransferEngine
    Note over D: 启动RecvingThread(负责P2P拉取)

    Note over R: start_health_checker(): 后台周期检查
    end

    rect rgb(255,250,230)
    Note over R,D_ZMQ: ===== 后台健康检查(每30-60s) =====

    loop 每 check_interval_secs
        R->>P: GET /health
        P-->>R: 200 OK / 超时
        R->>D: GET /health
        D-->>R: 200 OK / 超时
        Note over R: 连续失败>=3 -> set_healthy(false)
        Note over R: 连续成功>=2 -> set_healthy(true)
    end
    end

    rect rgb(245,240,255)
    Note over C,D_ZMQ: ===== 请求处理 =====

    C->>R: POST /v1/chat/completions

    Note over R: 同时选择P和D(发送任何请求前)
    Note over R: 过滤: is_available() = is_healthy() AND 熔断器可用

    Note over R: 构建Prefill请求: max_tokens=1, stream=false
    Note over R: kv_transfer_params={do_remote_decode:true, transfer_id}

    R->>P: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(max_tokens=1, kv_transfer_params)

    Note over P: 执行Prefill: embedding + 全部Transformer层
    Note over P: 生成KV Cache, 输出1个token
    Note over P: blocks暂不释放(等待D拉取完成后释放)

    P-->>R: 200 {kv_transfer_params: {<br/>remote_block_ids, remote_engine_id,<br/>remote_host, remote_port,<br/>remote_request_id}}

    Note over R: 构建Decode请求: 附加kv_transfer_params

    R->>D: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(原始max_tokens, kv_transfer_params={do_remote_prefill:true, ...})

    Note over D: 分配KV Cache blocks, 提交P2P拉取任务

    D_ZMQ->>P_ZMQ: ZMQ GET_META_MSG(请求NPU内存布局)
    P_ZMQ-->>D_ZMQ: MooncakeAgentMetadata<br/>(NPU基地址, te_rpc_port, block_lens)

    D_ZMQ->>RDMA: batch_transfer_sync_read<br/>(P2P RDMA: D直接从P的NPU内存拉取KV Cache)
    RDMA-->>D_ZMQ: 传输完成

    D_ZMQ->>P_ZMQ: ZMQ DONE_RECVING_MSG(通知P释放blocks)
    Note over P: 收到通知, 释放KV Cache blocks

    Note over D: KV加载完成, 跳过prefill, 开始decode

    loop 逐token流式输出
        D-->>R: Stream chunk
        R-->>C: SSE data
    end

    D-->>R: [DONE]
    R-->>C: [DONE]

    Note over R: 释放decode负载, 记录熔断器状态
    end
